dc_title_s: Chart exhibiting the discoveries of the second American Grinnell Expedition in search of Sir John Franklin
dc_description_s: 1 map ; 44 x 28 cm., folded to 16 x 10 cm.|Relief shown by hachures.|Shows locations of various fauna, huts, sea ice and glacciers.|Map is probably from his book "Arctic explorations: the second Grinnell expedition in search of Sir John Franklin, 1853, ’54, ’55".
